TEXT.S:
= u siwkay niza= Tao Ching Ying (1969.10.29) tatayna, nalecuhan i Taywan Taypak. u malimula' a ngangan sa ci Taoce. pahezekan i Taypak Cungsan Tatayna Teban a cacudadan. pahezekan i Kanatal Cengce Tabakiay a cacudadan, Sinbung a Si. u singanganay a tilibi palaw-ngatu telungay. matieng mudadiw, matineng misulit ku cudad, matineng misanga' ku palaw-ngatu. 1990 a mihcan, sakacacay a dadiw-balud mutahkal. ayzasa, u sakapahay a telungay ciniza. mitelung ku laziw a palaw-ngatu ciniza, kayadah a lawad. i Taywan a palaw-saliyut sa, u takalaway mitesekay a misakakawaway.
u sapuyaay a kakunizau kawaw nizau sulit nu Hulam1990
u sulit nu AmilikaMatilda Tao Ching-ying (Chinese: ; pinyin: Táo Jīngyíng) is a Taiwanese singer, television host and author. Tao graduated from National Chengchi University. In 2005, she married Taiwanese actor Lee Lee-zen.
